# DarkBot.Net — Clean Architecture

Desktop-бот для DarkOrbit: **WPF** + Frida bridge + Unity client.

## Слои

| Проект | Роль | Зависит от |
|--------|------|------------|
| `DarkBot.Net.Core` | `I*Api`, domain models, `Options/` | — |
| `DarkBot.Net.Application` | фасады, DTOs, Mappers, bot loop | Core |
| `DarkBot.Net.Infrastructure` | Frida, Unity, Login, Serilog, hosted sidecars | Core, Application |
| `DarkBot.Net.Presentation` | WPF, composition root | Application, Infrastructure |

```text
Presentation → Application (I*AppService), Infrastructure (только DI в Extensions/)
Infrastructure → Application, Core
Application → Core
```

## Application (desktop-фасады, без MediatR)

- `Contracts/I*AppService` — **единственный** API для ViewModels
- `DTOs/Responses/` — snapshot/DTO ответов (`BotStatusSnapshot`, …)
- `Mappers/` — domain/managers → DTO
- `Services/` — `*AppService` (orchestration)
- `BotEngine/` — internal tick loop, managers, state (не для VM)
- ❌ MediatR, WPF, UiStrings

Подробнее: правило `Application-Structure.mdc`.

## Infrastructure

- `Game/`, `Hosting/`, `Logging/` (`UseDarkBotSerilog`)
- ❌ ViewModels, XAML

## Presentation

- ViewModels → `I*AppService` + `Ui/*`
- `_botStatus.Capture()` → `DTOs.Responses.Bot` напрямую
- `Formatting/`, `Controls/Main/MapCanvas/` (render-only)
- ❌ `Services/`, `Models/`, `Mapping/`, дубли Application DTO

## AppService-фасады

`ILoginAppService` · `IGameLaunchAppService` · `IBotControlAppService` · `IBotStatusAppService` ·
`IGameConnectionStatusAppService` · `IMovementAppService` · `IAppShellAppService` · `IGameShutdownAppService`

## Запрещено

- ❌ ViewModel → Infrastructure / Manager / `IMovementApi`
- ❌ `Core → Infrastructure` (compile-time)
- ❌ MediatR в DarkBot.Net.Application
